Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE as the exclusive sales agents are pleased to present 41 The Centre, Forestville.

41 The Centre is a retail freehold conveniently situated within The Centre, Forestville, a busy pedestrian mall housing many big named tenants anchored by a Coles Supermarket. The property is currently tenanted by Japanese restaurant, Ichiban and  located in the heart of The Centre, servicing an affluent local catchment.

The property benefits from the following key
attributes:

- Building area of 74 sqm*
- Land area of 183 sqm*
- Suitable for owner occupiers and investors
- Large frontage over 6m to busy pedestrian strip mall
- Rear lane access with parking for 4 cars
- Currently tenanted by Japanese sushi restaurant Ichiban
- Located within a popular strip retail village anchored by  major tenants including Coles
- Zoned B2 Local Centre allowing for a variety of uses and further development (STCA) 
- Opposite Commonwealth Bank of Australia, Post Office, Domino's and Flight Centre
- Opportunity for alfresco seating area to be leased from council out the front of the shop
- The Centre is serviced by plenty of parking and transport for customer convenience

The property will be sold via online auction on Tuesday, 21 April 2020 at 12.00pm.
